paper_abstract: In this paper, we first introduce the definitions of the regularized derivative Green's function partial derivative(Z,l)G*(Z) and the discrete derivative Green's function partial derivative(Z,l)G(Z)(h) for the Poisson equation in five dimensions. Then the W-1,W-1-seminorm estimate for partial derivative(Z,l)G*(Z) is derived. Finally, applying the triangle inequality and the error estimate of the finite element approximation, we obtain the W-1,W-1-seminorm estimate with order O(vertical bar ln h vertical bar(7/5)) for partial derivative(Z,l)G(Z)(h).
paper_title: The W-1,W-1-Seminorm Estimate for the Discrete Derivative Green's Function for the 5D Poisson Equation
